OL,3,CGrandmother killed in motorbike crash
OL,4,Cwhile crossing road with grandchild
OL,6,FA woman in her 70s has died following
OL,7,Fa road traffic collision, which also
OL,8,Fleft her grandchild injured.
OL,10,FCumbria Police has now made an appeal
OL,11,Ffor witnesses following the fatal
OL,12,Fincident, which occurred on Ennerdale
OL,13,FRoad, Cleator Moor, at around 4.25pm
OL,14,Fon Tuesday 26 May.
OL,16,FThe woman was crossing the road with
OL,17,Fher grandchild when the pair was
OL,18,Fstruck by a motorbike.
