OL,3,CGrandmother killed in motorbike crash
OL,4,Cwhile crossing road with grandchild
OL,6,FThree men have since been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving.
OL,10,FThey are all from West Cumbria and
OL,11,Faged in their 20s.
OL,13,FCumbria Police is now looking for
OL,14,Fanyone who might have seen the
OL,15,Fincident to come forward, particularly
OL,16,Fanyone who might have seen the
OL,17,Fmotorbike.
OL,19,FIt is believed the motorbike was
OL,20,Ftravelling in convoy with two quad
OL,21,Fbikes before the collision.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
